<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-b7bf5a6f-daa7-45bc-9a7c-e46105d9b76f'>
            
<p class="">15.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-eae7cf87-0a6b-4c0c-b02d-c4726b2f80c8">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-eae7cf87-0a6b-4c0c-b02d-c4726b2f80c8">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-eae7cf87-0a6b-4c0c-b02d-c4726b2f80c8">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-eae7cf87-0a6b-4c0c-b02d-c4726b2f80c8">
                Mr. Beswick
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-eae7cf87-0a6b-4c0c-b02d-c4726b2f80c8" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-05-04/debates/e5136104-7e1a-4c29-b61c-041dbda4e3d7/TruceTalks#contribution-eae7cf87-0a6b-4c0c-b02d-c4726b2f80c8">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Secretary of State for Foreign Affairs if he will propose to the United Nations Command that a member of a State other than, and in addition to, the United States of America, should take part in the renewed truce talks in Korea.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-eae7cf87-0a6b-4c0c-b02d-c4726b2f80c8" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-05-04/debates/e5136104-7e1a-4c29-b61c-041dbda4e3d7/TruceTalks#contribution-eae7cf87-0a6b-4c0c-b02d-c4726b2f80c8">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-28602a99-4ced-4957-8f4e-ddde4d6fc67f">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-28602a99-4ced-4957-8f4e-ddde4d6fc67f">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-28602a99-4ced-4957-8f4e-ddde4d6fc67f">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-28602a99-4ced-4957-8f4e-ddde4d6fc67f">
                Mr. Nutting
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-28602a99-4ced-4957-8f4e-ddde4d6fc67f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-05-04/debates/e5136104-7e1a-4c29-b61c-041dbda4e3d7/TruceTalks#contribution-28602a99-4ced-4957-8f4e-ddde4d6fc67f">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">No, Sir. Her Majesty's Government see no reason to depart from the arrangements which have been followed since the talks first began in 1951.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-28602a99-4ced-4957-8f4e-ddde4d6fc67f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-05-04/debates/e5136104-7e1a-4c29-b61c-041dbda4e3d7/TruceTalks#contribution-28602a99-4ced-4957-8f4e-ddde4d6fc67f">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-66d64b5e-2043-4a03-9125-7b2490d24593">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-66d64b5e-2043-4a03-9125-7b2490d24593">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-66d64b5e-2043-4a03-9125-7b2490d24593">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-66d64b5e-2043-4a03-9125-7b2490d24593">
                Mr. Beswick
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-66d64b5e-2043-4a03-9125-7b2490d24593" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-05-04/debates/e5136104-7e1a-4c29-b61c-041dbda4e3d7/TruceTalks#contribution-66d64b5e-2043-4a03-9125-7b2490d24593">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Is not the hon. Gentleman aware of the very real and grave disquiet that there is at the handling of the truce talks on the United Nations side? If the Government want to cut <span id="11" class="column-number" data-column-number="11"></span> down the sniping at the U.S.A. to which the hon. Member for Farnham (Mr. Nicholson) referred last week cannot they get the U.S.A. to share their responsibility in this matter?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-66d64b5e-2043-4a03-9125-7b2490d24593" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-05-04/debates/e5136104-7e1a-4c29-b61c-041dbda4e3d7/TruceTalks#contribution-66d64b5e-2043-4a03-9125-7b2490d24593">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-22938303-f314-4611-ac9d-3ce765c6b18b">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-22938303-f314-4611-ac9d-3ce765c6b18b">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-22938303-f314-4611-ac9d-3ce765c6b18b">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-22938303-f314-4611-ac9d-3ce765c6b18b">
                Mr. Nutting
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-22938303-f314-4611-ac9d-3ce765c6b18b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-05-04/debates/e5136104-7e1a-4c29-b61c-041dbda4e3d7/TruceTalks#contribution-22938303-f314-4611-ac9d-3ce765c6b18b">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I think that the hon. Gentleman is being very much less than fair to the United Nations negotiators by the implication of his supplementary. General Harrison has concentrated, in the last few days, on securing a clarification of the Communist Command's proposals —proposals which have been by no means clear to me nor, I should imagine, to the hon. Gentleman. As he will have lately seen, the United Nations have now proposed that Pakistan should be the neutral State. In all the circumstances, I do not think that the attitude of the United Nations Command has been anything but wholly and remarkably reasonable and patient throughout many many months of arduous and tedious negotiations.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-22938303-f314-4611-ac9d-3ce765c6b18b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-05-04/debates/e5136104-7e1a-4c29-b61c-041dbda4e3d7/TruceTalks#contribution-22938303-f314-4611-ac9d-3ce765c6b18b">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-5e21befc-c928-4a76-9fb6-c84d31a18a06">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
