               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-05-04/debates/e5136104-7e1a-4c29-b61c-041dbda4e3d7/TruceTalks#contribution-5e21befc-c928-4a76-9fb6-c84d31a18a06">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Without desiring in any way to reflect on the delegation which the United Nations have had at the truce talks, may I ask whether it is not plain that it would be in the interests of everybody, including the United States of America, that responsibility for these negotiations should be shared more widely in view of the fact that the interests of all members of the United Nations are vitally affected by the result?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-5e21befc-c928-4a76-9fb6-c84d31a18a06" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-05-04/debates/e5136104-7e1a-4c29-b61c-041dbda4e3d7/TruceTalks#contribution-5e21befc-c928-4a76-9fb6-c84d31a18a06">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





