<p class="">I am sure that we would have a much better chance of getting a satisfactory solution under the conduct of General Harrison, who has been acting in accordance with instructions he received from higher authority, than we should have even if the hon. Lady volunteered herself to go.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
